Background: Opportunity Fund, with the motto - Working capital for working people, provides microfinance for small businesses and students. These loans prevent them from predatory lending and help them keep afloat when no financial institution is ready to help them. 

Objectve: The objective is to create an online loan calculator to embedd in the Opportunity Fund website (http://www.opportunityfund.org). This will be enable easy calculation of important details like APR, Equated payment amounts, total cost of loan etc. and also facilitate comparison between different loan terms offerings among lenders.

